workzen.xgen.model.website
Class Page

java.lang.Object
  workzen.xgen.model.website.Page

public class Page
extends java.lang.Object

Each page contains a reference to a menuitem. A Page provides access to an existing file in the filesystem. The path is created using the site's sourceBasePath, and the menuitem's href.
